br />\n<br />\n可惜，係早前，佢一切的勝利感已被徹底擊破，因為有一個人比佢更強，呢個人真正唔使戴住個膠袋，真正咁用其肉棒接觸到ck的粉紅隧道入面的每一mm肌膚，再係ck最完美的呻吟聲下，呢條友問ck，「可唔可以射入去」，伴隨住ck好急促的呼吸聲，ck答佢「射哂入來啦，全部比哂我」<br />\n<br />\n就係咁條友就一下一下咁，將佢d精一滴一滴咁射哂入ck最入最入的私處。痴漢雖然只係從個結果推論番成個場景出來，但係佢係呢一刻真正明白到，自己原來從來無勝利過，因為ck只肯比佢戴套屌，唔會留下任何留種的機會比佢，佢明白到真正的勝利，係條女可能比你搞大個肚，幫你留埋種，都肯比你真正中出，這才是真正勝利。<br />\n<br />\n呢個故事教訓我地，條女唔肯比你無套中出，唔肯比你射哂d精入去最入最入之處，根本未真正奉獻哂比你，對你仲有保留，你還不是真正的勝利者。<br />\n<br />\n你只會係他日中出你條女的那人，眼中的失敗者，永遠的失敗者。"},{"pid":"fcf0fa856fd353a5002b820b074f1682d1351ebd","tid":2319553,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"玩壞左既女人係好正"},{"pid":"729d2a0d7a9f39d93a76c6d019e2505e63b719d0","tid":2319553,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"白滑瘦底大波個樣又生得細個可愛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346e2fae162d93cbb216a1558c4658298f2ddd58","tid":2319553,"uid":62731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e32202bda789e936c3fd3bd5bc9a9e201835c1e","tid":2319553,"uid":173631,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7JMqFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7JMqFT.png&h=2f07b5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7LDMqFU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7LDMqFU.png&h=4673cb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8OTP7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8OTP7A.png&h=ab7c8cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGbuosB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGbuosB.png&h=816c7132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RWRBNB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RWRBNB.png&h=0078cd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKt1ezh.png\"